summary: Thief/Assassin player home Located near Windhelm.
descriptionHtml:
Cutpurse Cabin is my first mod created using the creation kit it adds a lakeside cabin near windhelm that includes trapdoors, storage, weapons, enchanting table, alchemy table, potion ingredients and a Dead senator that was outspoken against videogame violence... The readme included has more I have workedmost of the bugs out. Contact me with any questions you might have or suggestions for future mods for this type of character or others.
sody82@yahoo.com
You may add upon or use my mod in other mods just please give credit where credit is due. and notify me via email of the mod you are using it in so that I may download and ejoy it as well :)

NO DLC IS NEC.
author: JustinSoderquist   aka Lokisbuddy
